Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim INSTRUMENTO As String Dim INSTRUMENTO2 As String
INSTRUMENTO = Text63.Caption INSTRUMENTO2 = Text67.Caption PONTEIRO_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 4, 1) PONTEIRO_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 12, 1) PONTEIRO2_1 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 4, 1) PONTEIRO2_2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 12, 1)
If PONTEIRO_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 1) If PONTEIRO_2 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 5, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 13, 3) End If Else INSTR_TIPO = Left(INSTRUMENTO, 2) INSTR_NUMERO = Mid(INSTRUMENTO, 6, 8) End If
If PONTEIRO2_1 = "-" Then INSTR_TIPO2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO2, 1) If PONTEIRO2_2 <> "-" Then INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 5, 8) Else INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 5, 7) + "_" + Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 13, 3) End If Else INSTR_TIPO2 = Left(INSTRUMENTO2, 2) INSTR_NUMERO2 = Mid(INSTRUMENTO2, 6, 8) End If
'If INSTR_TIPO = "L" Then ' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "') And (EventSource LIKE 'H_' Or EventSource LIKE 'L_')" 'FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And (SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "%') And (SourceName LIKE '%LA%H_%' Or SourceName LIKE '%LA%L_%' or SourceName LIKE '%LA%HH_%' Or SourceName LIKE '%LA%LL_%')" 'Else AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_TIPO & "' And (EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & INSTR_NUMERO2 & "')" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & INSTR_NUMERO & "%'" 'End If
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_CV_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F2}" End If
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_CV1_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F2}" End If
End Sub
